1
00:01:35,979 --> 00:01:38,220
[Too Young To Love]

2
00:01:38,479 --> 00:01:41,229
[Episode 11]

3
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,120
When did you learn to...

4
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,040
Hush.

5
00:02:07,650 --> 00:02:08,380
Draw a card.

6
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,000
What does this mean?

7
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,840
The Wheel of Fortune.

8
00:02:26,290 --> 00:02:28,210
Your Mr. Right has appeared.

9
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,820
He's someone near you.

10
00:02:38,650 --> 00:02:40,710
[Hailan University]

11
00:02:38,730 --> 00:02:41,740
Xiaole, Ning and I
got into Hailan University as we wished.

12
00:02:40,810 --> 00:02:43,340
♪ She left in spring ♪

13
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,579
Xiaole joined the photography club

14
00:02:43,579 --> 00:02:46,610
and instantly became
the new prince charming on campus.

15
00:02:44,170 --> 00:02:47,090
♪ Gone with her was cherry blossoms ♪

16
00:02:46,390 --> 00:02:48,410
[Welcome, freshmen]

17
00:02:46,770 --> 00:02:49,120
Ning and Chen Fan
started a campus romance.

18
00:02:47,770 --> 00:02:50,329
♪ On the once youthful face ♪

19
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:51,910
But Ning is so busy practicing the cello
every day that she has no time for dates.

20
00:02:51,410 --> 00:02:54,040
♪ I can't help but think of her ♪

21
00:02:51,970 --> 00:02:54,790
Zhao Zhenghao went to college
in another city. As for Mengmeng,

22
00:02:54,790 --> 00:02:58,350
she blossomed as college began
and fit right in.

23
00:02:54,970 --> 00:02:57,260
♪ She left in spring ♪

24
00:02:58,410 --> 00:03:02,600
We all finally started the college life
we had always dreamed of.

25
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:00,850
♪ All was like a dream ♪

26
00:03:01,830 --> 00:03:04,410
♪ Youth never lasts ♪

27
00:03:05,870 --> 00:03:08,430
♪ Just let her go ♪

28
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,290
Look over there.

29
00:03:09,490 --> 00:03:11,720
♪ The paper plane that was once set free ♪

30
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:15,270
♪ Will find its way back
to the old desk and chair at school ♪

31
00:03:15,310 --> 00:03:17,680
Okay. Lift up your head a bit.

32
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:18,550
♪ All stories have yet to end ♪

33
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,150
That's right.

34
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,700
A little lower.

35
00:03:26,710 --> 00:03:28,210
Mengmeng!

36
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,030
Lan!

37
00:03:29,510 --> 00:03:31,190
Look at your new haircut.

38
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,470
So pretty.

39
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:33,840
I used a curly iron.

40
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,520
I'll fix your hair next time.

41
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:34,840
Great!

42
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,340
Why is Ning absent again?

43
00:03:36,470 --> 00:03:38,360
Is she having another practice session?

44
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,470
She's working too hard.

45
00:03:39,470 --> 00:03:41,030
I should practice the cello too.

46
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:41,680
Ning isn't here.

47
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:44,010
So you got all dressed up for nothing,
huh?

48
00:03:44,030 --> 00:03:44,750
Wait.

49
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,840
You're in a blue shirt,

50
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,520
and...

51
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,360
deep blue pants.

52
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,190
A lovely match

53
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:49,840
with a dash of red as decoration.

54
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,770
Well, you must be

55
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:52,010
up to something.

56
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,079
Up to what?

57
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:55,560
You should spend this time with Ning

58
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,760
instead of gossiping, don't you think?

59
00:03:59,079 --> 00:03:59,850
Oh right.

60
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:04,340
There will be an event in your university
this Saturday...

61
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,240
[Freshman Dance]

62
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,490
The Freshman Dance.

63
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,190
My girlfriend Ning will perform

64
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:11,580
the opening number

65
00:04:11,630 --> 00:04:13,290
as a freshman representative.

66
00:04:13,290 --> 00:04:15,420
This is a tradition of our university.

67
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:18,550
But the rule of the dance says

68
00:04:18,579 --> 00:04:21,480
each participant must bring
a partner of the opposite gender.

69
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,360
This is clearly

70
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,810
a mixer, isn't it?

71
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,070
Your university

72
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:27,630
is just too...

73
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:30,500
focused on social events
and not academics.

74
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:32,360
But as I heard,

75
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:35,360
we can invite those from other colleges
to this dance.

76
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:38,530
Didn't your sweetheart Luo Ningzi
tell you that?

77
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,070
Ning has been busy since college started.

78
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:44,510
She hasn't told me about the dance yet.

79
00:04:44,870 --> 00:04:46,000
You little wimp.

80
00:04:46,420 --> 00:04:49,020
I just wasted my time
getting you all dolled up.

81
00:04:49,070 --> 00:04:51,070
Ning's probably busy practicing the cello.

82
00:04:51,070 --> 00:04:52,000
I need to go practice too.

83
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:52,560
Time to take off.

84
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,020
Bye bye!

85
00:05:09,990 --> 00:05:12,270
[The school piano is broken again]

86
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,160
Professor Ye,

87
00:05:16,750 --> 00:05:18,310
I wonder if I can ask you a question.

88
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:19,870
Do you have time now?

89
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:23,440
Let's talk outside.

90
00:05:29,190 --> 00:05:30,870
Only one student can receive

91
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:32,310
the full scholarship every year.

92
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:34,370
I'll send you the information later.

93
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,050
Professor Ye,

94
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:38,050
I'll possibly be chosen, won't I?

95
00:05:38,070 --> 00:05:39,950
Academic performance
is not the only criteria.

96
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:42,210
The evaluation covers many other areas.

97
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:43,190
I think you should attend

98
00:05:43,190 --> 00:05:44,430
more extracurricular activities

99
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:45,490
in your spare time.

100
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:46,750
Got it.

101
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:53,240
You've been absent-minded
in the cello practice lately.

102
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:55,000
Did something happen at home?

103
00:05:57,310 --> 00:05:58,770
I'll get myself together.

104
00:05:59,310 --> 00:06:01,510
If you have encountered difficulties,

105
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,730
just let me know.

106
00:06:03,190 --> 00:06:04,850
I'll help you find a solution.

107
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:07,010
Thanks, Professor Ye.

108
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:08,360
I think I can manage.

109
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,430
You're remarkably gifted,

110
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:15,560
with the potential of being a cellist.

111
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,690
Do cherish your talent.

112
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:20,360
Yes.

113
00:06:36,550 --> 00:06:37,090
Ning,

114
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,730
I finally found you.

115
00:06:38,750 --> 00:06:39,680
I went to the practice room for you,

116
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,240
but a classmate of yours said
you were in the library.

117
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,180
So I came here.

118
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,780
I brought you food.

119
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,950
Don't you have a class to attend?

120
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:48,870
It won't begin in another hour.

121
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:51,159
You didn't reply my messages,

122
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:52,159
so I came find you.

123
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,870
I've been occupied lately,

124
00:06:54,870 --> 00:06:56,000
and my phone's always on mute.

125
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,750
Maybe I didn't notice your texts.

126
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:58,630
It's okay.

127
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,010
I'm having a class soon.

128
00:07:01,750 --> 00:07:02,280
Oh right.

129
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:05,560
There's a freshman dance on our campus
this Saturday.

130
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,680
Would you be my partner?

131
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,310
Sure.

132
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:09,390
I'd love to.

133
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:10,840
Let's go.

134
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,510
I'm feeling great...

135
00:07:26,740 --> 00:07:28,110
Hey, nice kick.

136
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:30,040
Shan!

137
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:30,870
Shan!

138
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:32,070
What brings you here?

139
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:34,070
-I asked Shan to come over.
-What's up? How may I help?

140
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:35,190
What is so important

141
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:36,510
that you couldn't say on the phone?

142
00:07:36,510 --> 00:07:37,350
Shan,

143
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,820
will you do me a favour?

144
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:41,210
There's freshman dance tomorrow night.

145
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:43,370
Entries must be mixed-gender pairs.

146
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:44,110
Could you...

147
00:07:44,159 --> 00:07:45,090
be my date for it?

148
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,120
Then what about Xiaole?

149
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:48,560
He...

150
00:07:48,909 --> 00:07:50,360
He's adored by many girls.

151
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:52,890
I'd hate to be the envy of every girl
on campus.

152
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,060
Okay.

153
00:07:54,190 --> 00:07:55,240
On one condition, though.

154
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,750
You must buy me
the most expansive beverage here.

155
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:58,409
No problem!

156
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,090
Let's go.

157
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:01,580
Sure!

158
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:13,490
I didn't expect you'd hide such a secret
deep inside.

159
00:08:15,070 --> 00:08:15,630
What?

160
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:19,090
If you invite me to the dance,

161
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:21,510
I'll help you find out if Lan is into you.

162
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:24,080
Stop talking nonsense.

163
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:28,750
Why do you want to go to
our school's freshman dance?

164
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:30,350
Will you bring me to it or not?

165
00:08:30,630 --> 00:08:31,290
No, I won't.

166
00:08:34,309 --> 00:08:34,809
Fine.

167
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,530
It's a deal now.

168
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,790
Lan!

169
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:49,200
-What is it?
-I'll attend the freshman dance too!

170
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,320
Really?

171
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,550
I'm spinning and dancing.

172
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:59,080
Let me do the spin.

173
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:03,590
[To the future we go,
with you in my youth]

174
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:15,620
When did Shan learn to dance?

175
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,530
I have no idea.

176
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:19,920
[To the future we go,
with you in my youth]

177
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:45,910
[To the future we go,
with you in my youth]

178
00:09:47,950 --> 00:09:49,990
[To the future we go,
with you in my youth]

179
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:17,280
[To the future we go,
with you in my youth]

180
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:28,980
[To the future we go,
with you in my youth]

181
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:29,030
Let's thank these three handsome lads
for their wonderful performance!

182
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:31,840
Next,

183
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,720
let's welcome...

184
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,550
the freshman representative
of the cello major,

185
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:36,600
Ms. Luo Ningzi.

186
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:39,200
She will treat us to a cello solo!

187
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:43,260
[Hailan University Freshmen Dance]

188
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,260
Let's welcome her!

189
00:10:58,700 --> 00:11:01,540
[Hailan University Freshmen Dance]

190
00:11:57,710 --> 00:12:03,030
[Hailan University Freshmen Dance]

191
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,080
Again, let's thank

192
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,200
Ms. Luo Ningzi

193
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:19,600
for such a beautiful cello solo!

194
00:12:22,270 --> 00:12:23,550
Our next performer

195
00:12:23,670 --> 00:12:26,910
is the freshman representative
of the Department of Photography,

196
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:27,960
Mr. Tong Xiaole.

197
00:12:28,550 --> 00:12:29,610
Let's welcome him!

198
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:32,390
-You're stunning!
-Stunning!

199
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:35,700
Senior, I didn't prepare a performance.

200
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,390
I believe it's known to all of us

201
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:40,360
that Mr. Tong Xiaole

202
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:42,750
got higher grades than any other freshman

203
00:12:43,030 --> 00:12:44,320
this year,

204
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:46,670
and that he chose the photography major.

205
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:48,080
We are all curious.

206
00:12:48,390 --> 00:12:50,390
Did you choose Hailan University

207
00:12:50,790 --> 00:12:52,390
for a special reason?

208
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,680
There was no special reason.

209
00:12:58,790 --> 00:13:00,720
Was it because of your girlfriend?

210
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,960
We are all wondering about that.

211
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,060
Xiaole, do you have a girlfriend?

212
00:13:08,670 --> 00:13:10,600
Sorry to disappoint you.

213
00:13:10,910 --> 00:13:12,370
I don't have a girlfriend.

214
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,720
But there is indeed a girl in my heart.

215
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:22,720
Who is she?

216
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:25,320
He was into a girl in high school.

217
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:27,720
Who was that girl?

218
00:13:27,790 --> 00:13:28,540
I don't know.

219
00:13:28,670 --> 00:13:30,270
Alright. That was only a joke.

220
00:13:30,270 --> 00:13:33,060
Here comes the last show.

221
00:13:33,270 --> 00:13:37,320
Let's give a warm welcome
to the seniors of the dance major

222
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,200
and their performance!

223
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:41,320
After that,
you'll have some free time to yourselves!

224
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:53,960
Good for you, for having a secret crush!

225
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:54,720
Shh.

226
00:13:56,670 --> 00:13:58,090
I bet she'll be shocked

227
00:13:58,200 --> 00:13:59,270
when she learns the truth.

228
00:13:59,270 --> 00:13:59,980
Be quiet.

229
00:14:10,850 --> 00:14:11,800
Hello.

230
00:14:12,090 --> 00:14:14,750
I’m Xia Han
from the Department of String Music.

231
00:14:15,270 --> 00:14:16,270
My name is Chen Fan.

232
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:17,920
But I don't go to this university.

233
00:14:17,920 --> 00:14:18,840
It's not a problem.

234
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:21,080
My friends and I are going to karaoke
this week.

235
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,940
Will you join us, if you have time?

236
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:26,000
Sorry, I'll be occupied.

237
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:27,320
It's okay.

238
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:28,440
Let's exchange contacts

239
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,370
and meet up when you're available.

240
00:14:33,910 --> 00:14:34,670
Excuse me.

241
00:14:38,850 --> 00:14:40,260
Shall we dance?

242
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,270
Sure.

243
00:15:18,790 --> 00:15:20,190
Are you looking for Shan?

244
00:15:21,250 --> 00:15:23,320
He disappeared after a dance.

245
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:26,750
It seems...

246
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:28,000
he has indeed

247
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:30,350
been out of sight since that dance.

248
00:15:43,030 --> 00:15:43,720
Chen!

249
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,140
What's up, Xiaole?

250
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,480
This is my high school classmate.

251
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:50,540
I'm Qiao Mengmeng!

252
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,550
Her name is Qiao Mengmeng.

253
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:54,610
This is her first visit to our campus.

254
00:15:54,790 --> 00:15:57,200
He's senior to me
in the Department of Photography,

255
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,130
named Chen Chen.

256
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,090
Hello, Senior Chen.

257
00:16:00,270 --> 00:16:00,670
Hello.

258
00:16:01,670 --> 00:16:04,600
Why don't you... give her a tour?

259
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,670
Sure, of course.

260
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:08,550
Lan,

261
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:11,330
I'd rather stay out of this dancing stuff.

262
00:16:11,670 --> 00:16:12,600
You two have fun.

263
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:14,080
Bye.

264
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:23,790
What's your hobby, Senior?

265
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:24,550
I...

266
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:26,390
just enjoy taking photos.

267
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:28,030
I see.

268
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:36,320
It seems we've been left alone

269
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:38,200
on this lovely dance night.

270
00:16:42,790 --> 00:16:43,440
Well...

271
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,410
Will you do me the honor?

272
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:47,320
Sure.

273
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,180
The other hand.

274
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:56,200
Oh.

275
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:07,079
Spill it.

276
00:17:07,310 --> 00:17:08,240
What do you want?

277
00:17:09,310 --> 00:17:11,910
You know I attend this event every year,
right?

278
00:17:14,310 --> 00:17:15,200
Don't get me wrong.

279
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:16,440
Today, I came here only to h-help

280
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,109
Yi Lan.

281
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:20,890
Still as straightforward as ever.

282
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:24,560
I've just learned
how to communicate with you.

283
00:17:26,500 --> 00:17:27,099
Hey, wait.

284
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:29,960
Has your dream come true?

285
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:35,300
It's none of your business, is it?

286
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:41,400
W-What

287
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:42,920
is your hobby then?

288
00:17:43,030 --> 00:17:43,960
Me?

289
00:17:44,510 --> 00:17:48,030
I enjoy taking a walk and watching movies.

290
00:17:48,030 --> 00:17:49,560
Sometimes I come visit Lan.

291
00:17:50,510 --> 00:17:51,440
But as you know,

292
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:53,200
watching movies alone is boring.

293
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:55,660
We can go to the cinema together
if possible.

294
00:17:55,750 --> 00:17:56,270
Sure.

295
00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:00,200
Thank you for coming today.

296
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,200
I've had much fun.

297
00:18:03,110 --> 00:18:04,110
Don't mention it.

298
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:05,160
Our schools

299
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:07,270
are close anyway.

300
00:18:07,750 --> 00:18:08,550
In the future,

301
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:10,000
I can be with you

302
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,020
for breakfast,

303
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:12,110
lunch,

304
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:13,350
dinner,

305
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:15,320
and even late-night snacks.

306
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:16,680
However...

307
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:19,410
I may have to bail on breakfast,

308
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:22,940
since I can't get up early in the morning.

309
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:29,220
Join me for lunch then.

310
00:18:29,270 --> 00:18:31,270
I might be busy at night.

311
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:34,590
Okay.

312
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:36,270
Then...

313
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:39,960
See you tomorrow at noon.

314
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:40,290
Sure.

315
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:03,270
When did you learn to dance?

316
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:05,350
I get the hang

317
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,920
of everything after a mere glance.

318
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,270
Cut it out!

319
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:11,810
Senior,

320
00:19:12,480 --> 00:19:14,140
take photos of Xiaole and Lan.

321
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:20,810
Don't you think...

322
00:19:21,110 --> 00:19:22,510
they are a perfect match?

323
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,440
I do think so.

324
00:19:55,030 --> 00:19:58,810
[Campus Photo Contest]

325
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:57,350
This year's photo contest is approaching.

326
00:19:57,350 --> 00:19:58,350
Will you go for it?

327
00:20:02,110 --> 00:20:03,000
Is it true that you have

328
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:05,730
a social media account
with a million followers?

329
00:20:06,830 --> 00:20:07,880
It's just a rumor,

330
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:08,880
an exaggeration.

331
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:12,160
Impressive.

332
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:13,720
Now I get it.

333
00:20:14,510 --> 00:20:16,680
No wonder many girls are joining
the photography club lately.

334
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:18,010
I bet they all aim at you.

335
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:31,890
You like her?

336
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:34,370
Give it to me.

337
00:20:49,350 --> 00:20:49,920
Lan.

338
00:20:51,480 --> 00:20:52,640
What's on your mind?

339
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:55,960
Xiaoyi.

340
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:56,350
Yes?

341
00:20:56,350 --> 00:20:57,350
I have a question.

342
00:20:58,270 --> 00:20:59,270
How...

343
00:20:59,270 --> 00:21:01,480
did you feel when you fell in love

344
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:02,680
with your boyfriend?

345
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:06,240
I felt...

346
00:21:06,270 --> 00:21:08,960
that my heart was beating fast.

347
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:11,920
You'll know it when you fall in love.

348
00:21:16,160 --> 00:21:17,880
Well, I need to go on a date.

349
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:19,920
My boyfriend is waiting for me.

350
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:21,450
Aren't you leaving with me?

351
00:21:22,270 --> 00:21:23,400
He's right over there.

352
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:23,880
Bye bye!

353
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:24,900
See you.

354
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:31,240
The heart beats fast...

355
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:41,000
Lan!

356
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:43,160
What are you doing here?

357
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:45,160
Why are you here, Shan?

358
00:21:45,350 --> 00:21:45,920
I...

359
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:47,660
was delivering an accessory.

360
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:48,400
Shan.

361
00:21:49,030 --> 00:21:50,960
Where did you go during the freshman dance
yesterday?

362
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:52,420
I couldn't find you at all.

363
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:54,590
I left early for an emergency

364
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:55,590
before I could tell you.

365
00:21:55,590 --> 00:21:55,990
Got it.

366
00:21:57,400 --> 00:21:58,930
You don't have an umbrella?

367
00:21:59,160 --> 00:22:00,480
Let me walk you back to your dorm.

368
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:00,880
Okay.

369
00:22:00,900 --> 00:22:01,440
Let's go.

370
00:22:12,070 --> 00:22:12,870
Come on, move.

371
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:34,960
Your Mr. Right has appeared.

372
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:37,480
He's someone near you.

373
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:54,640
What are your plans for the weekend?

374
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:55,830
Dates?

375
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:59,510
Of course. Such a lovely weekend
should be spent outside.

376
00:23:01,310 --> 00:23:03,970
Why don't you go out
with your boyfriend Xiaole?

377
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:04,960
Let me say this again:

378
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:06,270
Xiaole is not my boyfriend.

379
00:23:06,270 --> 00:23:07,730
He's my childhood friend.

380
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:09,140
I'm not seeing anyone.

381
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:14,410
I'm leaving.

382
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:15,130
-Bye.
-Bye.

383
00:23:15,150 --> 00:23:15,920
Bye bye.

384
00:23:22,370 --> 00:23:25,740
[Millionaires-to-be]

385
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:25,270
Any plans, guys?

386
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:27,260
Shall we hang out this afternoon?

387
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:34,510
Today marks the beginning of the romance
between me and Chen.

388
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:36,400
You have a boyfriend now?

389
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:39,350
That's really fast.

390
00:23:40,510 --> 00:23:41,880
We're on a date.

391
00:23:49,350 --> 00:23:59,150
[Humph, sickeningly sweet]

392
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:51,070
Sickeningly sweet.

393
00:24:14,110 --> 00:24:14,720
Let's go.

394
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:23,160
Are you going to meet Shan in this dress?

395
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:24,720
What's wrong?

396
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:25,930
It's pretty.

397
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:31,850
As your friend,

398
00:24:31,870 --> 00:24:33,950
I feel obligated to suggest you

399
00:24:34,510 --> 00:24:35,790
wear something else.

400
00:24:36,030 --> 00:24:37,640
Or you might scare Shan.

401
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:42,450
It's none of your business!

402
00:24:46,830 --> 00:24:48,510
I already offered my advice!

403
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:55,000
Shan.

404
00:24:55,590 --> 00:24:56,050
You're here.

405
00:24:56,050 --> 00:24:56,440
Yes.

406
00:24:57,260 --> 00:24:57,890
So am I.

407
00:24:59,350 --> 00:25:00,480
Don't you feel cold?

408
00:25:00,790 --> 00:25:01,390
Not at all.

409
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:02,830
Okay.

410
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:43,200
What now?

411
00:26:02,110 --> 00:26:03,240
What are you trying to do, Tong Xiaole?

412
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:04,820
You have a death wish or what?

413
00:26:04,820 --> 00:26:06,510
Didn't you say you wanted to study here?

414
00:26:06,510 --> 00:26:07,220
Step aside!

415
00:26:07,390 --> 00:26:08,120
Not a chance.

416
00:26:11,590 --> 00:26:12,240
Lan!

417
00:26:12,960 --> 00:26:13,590
What is it?

418
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:15,200
I'd like to give you something.

419
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:16,060
Do it here then.

420
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:18,830
The thing's over there.
Come get it with me.

421
00:26:18,830 --> 00:26:19,880
You go get it yourself.

422
00:26:19,880 --> 00:26:20,920
It's too heavy to be carried alone.

423
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:21,960
-Help me with it.
-I'm sure you can manage.

424
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:22,400
Just come help...

425
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:23,460
What are you doing?

426
00:26:26,030 --> 00:26:26,720
Well,

427
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,680
the AC is on.

428
00:26:29,160 --> 00:26:30,200
Take this blanket.

429
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,260
Don't catch a cold.

430
00:26:32,110 --> 00:26:32,480
Okay.

431
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:35,500
There's water. Help yourselves.

432
00:26:59,270 --> 00:26:59,880
Lan,

433
00:27:00,270 --> 00:27:01,680
don't you always want to read this issue?

434
00:27:00,350 --> 00:27:03,760
[Comic Party]

435
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:02,760
Who said that?

436
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:04,100
Get it away!

437
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:08,680
Shan,

438
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:09,200
it's her fault.

439
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:09,830
No, his fault.

440
00:27:09,830 --> 00:27:10,400
Her fault.

441
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,060
Your fault!

442
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:15,240
Sorry, Shan.

443
00:27:15,360 --> 00:27:16,110
How about this?

444
00:27:16,110 --> 00:27:18,270
Let's go buy ice cream for Shan
as an apology.

445
00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:19,270
My idea's better.

446
00:27:19,270 --> 00:27:22,270
Why don't you go buy ice cream
for us both as an apology?

447
00:27:23,510 --> 00:27:25,200
If any instruments break down
at your school,

448
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:27,130
a repair guy will be needed, right?

449
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:29,400
Several students have indeed asked for

450
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:31,130
some shared cellos to be fixed.

451
00:27:31,240 --> 00:27:31,880
Then I...

452
00:27:33,330 --> 00:27:35,260
I can offer discounts for that.

453
00:27:35,830 --> 00:27:36,830
I'll ask the school about it.

454
00:27:36,830 --> 00:27:37,030
O-Okay.

455
00:27:37,030 --> 00:27:37,560
Go ahead.

456
00:27:45,270 --> 00:27:45,720
Lan,

457
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:47,960
I remember
that teacher of your department...

458
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:50,560
Professor Ye, has been single forever,
right?

459
00:27:50,680 --> 00:27:51,510
You mean Professor Ye Mei?

460
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:51,910
Yes.

461
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:54,060
She's a dedicated bachelorette.

462
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:58,270
I see. So she won't get married.

463
00:27:58,700 --> 00:28:01,030
No wonder she has achieved so many things.

464
00:28:02,200 --> 00:28:02,750
Nothing happened.

465
00:28:02,750 --> 00:28:03,150
You...

466
00:28:03,240 --> 00:28:03,440
g-go on

467
00:28:03,440 --> 00:28:03,750
with

468
00:28:03,830 --> 00:28:04,360
the talk.

469
00:28:06,030 --> 00:28:06,610
Lan,

470
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:08,960
didn't you say you'd practice the cello
today?

471
00:28:08,960 --> 00:28:10,440
That can wait.

472
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:11,800
What if you fail the tryout

473
00:28:11,800 --> 00:28:13,920
and can't attend
Professor Ye Mei's lectures?

474
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:15,050
You needs practice.

475
00:28:16,350 --> 00:28:17,350
Xiaole is right.

476
00:28:17,750 --> 00:28:18,720
Don't come here tomorrow.

477
00:28:18,720 --> 00:28:19,960
Focus on the cello practice.

478
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:21,480
No, I can still come here, Shan.

479
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:23,440
You should prioritize your practice.

480
00:28:23,440 --> 00:28:23,900
Xiaole!

481
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:26,480
Keep watch on her.

482
00:28:28,590 --> 00:28:29,120
Let's go.

483
00:28:30,350 --> 00:28:30,680
Move.

484
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:38,030
Next, Candidate No. 6.

485
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:41,110
Candidate No. 7, please get ready.

486
00:28:48,440 --> 00:28:49,920
Are you okay?

487
00:28:50,350 --> 00:28:51,350
I need to go to...

488
00:28:52,110 --> 00:28:53,160
the infirmary.

489
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:54,060
The infirmary?

490
00:28:54,750 --> 00:28:56,150
Is your stomach hurting?

491
00:28:57,920 --> 00:28:58,480
Ning,

492
00:28:59,110 --> 00:29:00,840
I'll take her to the infirmary.

493
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,880
It'll be my turn soon.

494
00:29:02,960 --> 00:29:04,440
And you're right behind me.

495
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:05,440
I'll be back soon.

496
00:29:06,240 --> 00:29:07,900
Make it in time for the tryout!

497
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:11,770
Next, Candidate No. 7.

498
00:29:11,960 --> 00:29:14,640
Candidate No. 8, please get ready.

499
00:29:22,510 --> 00:29:23,680
What took you so long?

500
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:24,740
The tryout is over.

501
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:26,270
It's over?

502
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:27,000
Yes.

503
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:29,000
That girl is a stranger to you.

504
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,200
But she was in agony

505
00:29:30,370 --> 00:29:31,970
for acute gastroenteritis.

506
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:34,030
Fine.

507
00:29:34,680 --> 00:29:35,960
I'm off to my part-time job.

508
00:29:35,960 --> 00:29:36,350
Okay.

509
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:48,680
Professor Ye.

510
00:29:49,590 --> 00:29:51,880
Late comers
are automatically disqualified.

511
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:53,260
I told you guys before.

512
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:55,830
Can I attend next year's tryout?

513
00:29:57,960 --> 00:30:00,290
Then you'll have a slim chance of passing.

514
00:30:04,360 --> 00:30:06,020
Why do you want to learn cello?

515
00:30:08,750 --> 00:30:09,910
It's a way...

516
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:11,480
for me to feel,

517
00:30:12,110 --> 00:30:13,570
to have joy, and to express

518
00:30:14,110 --> 00:30:14,960
my thoughts.

519
00:30:16,890 --> 00:30:18,960
Not for the admission to a top orchestra

520
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:20,690
and a chance to get on the stage?

521
00:30:22,960 --> 00:30:24,560
Of course I want all that too.

522
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:26,410
I would love to have more people

523
00:30:26,510 --> 00:30:27,590
hear my music.

524
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:32,720
You actually excel in expressing emotions
through music.

525
00:30:33,440 --> 00:30:35,110
But your basic skills are poor.

526
00:30:35,110 --> 00:30:36,960
Have more practice in that regard.

527
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:37,690
Understood?

528
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:38,440
Yes.

529
00:30:38,590 --> 00:30:39,990
Thank you, Professor Ye.

530
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:41,160
I'm leaving then.

531
00:31:12,880 --> 00:31:14,880
You're tired from running a few steps?

532
00:31:14,880 --> 00:31:17,200
You've neglected your 5k running training
due to the cello practice, right?

533
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:18,010
Listen,

534
00:31:18,110 --> 00:31:20,120
I was really happy today.

535
00:31:20,240 --> 00:31:21,750
Professor Ye gave me a praise

536
00:31:21,750 --> 00:31:24,550
just when I thought
I'd never have a second chance.

537
00:31:24,770 --> 00:31:26,960
You're so cheerful
though you failed the tryout.

538
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:28,350
I can attend it next year.

539
00:31:28,350 --> 00:31:30,000
At least now I know I have a shot.

540
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:32,530
As a reward to myself,
I'll rest for a few days.

541
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:35,200
Have you...

542
00:31:36,570 --> 00:31:37,780
met with Shan lately?

543
00:31:38,680 --> 00:31:39,110
Yes.

544
00:31:39,350 --> 00:31:41,110
Just the other day
he delivered an accessory here,

545
00:31:41,110 --> 00:31:42,160
I ran into him.

546
00:31:42,480 --> 00:31:43,610
Then what happened?

547
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:44,680
Well, then...

548
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:50,240
Hey,

549
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:52,010
can I ask you a question?

550
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:56,920
How did you realize

551
00:31:58,030 --> 00:32:00,030
you fell in love with that girl?

552
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:01,650
What do you mean?

553
00:32:02,150 --> 00:32:02,530
Well,

554
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:04,240
I'm wondering if your heart

555
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:04,880
also

556
00:32:04,960 --> 00:32:07,160
pounded like crazy.

557
00:32:08,110 --> 00:32:08,640
"Also"?

558
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:14,540
Do you have a crush on someone now?

559
00:32:16,350 --> 00:32:17,030
Well...

560
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:19,610
Just a little situation in my life.

561
00:32:24,160 --> 00:32:25,200
Stop prying!
